# RGBJunkie effects API

See **`EFFECTS_API.md`**.

- **Catalog:** `GET /effects-catalog.json` — each row has **`contentUrl`** (JSON) and **`exportPlainUrl`** (builder with **`exportPlain=1`**).
- **Effect JSON:** `GET /effects/effect.json?id=…` — **`html`** is always **`null`**; use **`exportPlainUrl`** in the browser for **`.txt` download + `<pre>`**.
- **Plain text URL line:** `GET /effects/effect-export-url.txt?id=…` returns **`text/plain`** with one line = **`exportPlainUrl`** (for `curl`; not the HTML body).
- **`includeWorkspace=1`** on effect.json adds large **`workspace`** for debugging only.

When changing export behavior, keep **`runPlainTextExportDownload`** in **`js/main.js`** aligned with **`buildExportPayload`**.
